The '''''Respite''''' was a [[Hospital ship/Legends|hospital ship]] of the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref> It was present at the [[Battle of Praesitlyn]]. Its complement included [[Bacta tank/Legends|bacta tanks]] and skin-regeneration equipment.

